%% Diagram: Vector Clock Trace
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant P1 as P1
    participant P2 as P2
    participant P3 as P3

    Note over P1: [1,0,0]
    P1->>P2: msg ([1,0,0])
    Note over P2: [1,1,0]
    Note over P3: [0,0,1]
    Note over P3: [0,0,2]
    P2->>P3: msg ([1,1,0])
    Note over P3: merge → [1,1,3]
    P1->>P2: msg ([2,0,0])
    Note over P2: merge → [2,2,0]

    Note right of P3: P2 [2,2,0] vs P3 [1,1,3] are concurrent — 2>1 but 0<3. Vector clocks detect this. Lamport cannot.
